        "This program: (Travel Time Estimator)\n",
        "Ask the user to enter the distance between two cities in miles.\n",
        "\n",
        "Ask the user to enter their planned speed in miles per hour.\n",
        "\n",
        "Divide the distance by the speed to calculate travel time in hours.\n",
        "\n",
        "Print the travel time so the user can see how long the trip will take."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "lwiGS8RDpY5M"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "S_Kiavn9pTkb"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "distance = float(input(\"Enter the distance between the cities (in miles): \"))\n",
        "speed = float(input(\"Enter your speed (in miles per hour): \"))\n",
        "travel_time = distance / speed\n",
        "print(\"Estimated travel time (in hours):\", travel_time)\n"
      ],
