        "This program: (Paint Cost Estimator)\n",
        "\n",
        "Asks for the size of the room in square feet\n",
        "\n",
        "Asks for the cost of paint per square foot\n",
        "\n",
        "Multiplies the two values to get total cost\n",
        "\n",
        "Prints the total cost of painting the room"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "70Fi0ahw1te-"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "room_size = float(input(\"Enter the size of the room in square feet: \"))\n",
        "paint_cost_per_sqft = float(input(\"Enter the cost of paint per square foot: \"))\n",
        "total_paint_cost = room_size * paint_cost_per_sqft\n",
        "print(\"Total paint cost is:\", total_paint_cost)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
